<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />Satisfy us in the morning with your covenant faithfulness</para>

<para style="q1">so that we may rejoice and be glad all our days.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />Make us glad in proportion to the days you afflicted us</para>

<para style="q1">and to the years we have experienced trouble.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />Let your servants see your work,</para>

<para style="q1">and let our children see your majesty.</para>
